| Command            | What it does                                                       |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `mkcert -install`  | Creates and installs a trusted local Certificate Authority (CA)    |
| `mkcert localhost` | Generates trusted `cert.pem` and `key.pem` signed by your local CA |

mkcert local.dev 127.0.0.1 ::1

mkcert offline.mahis 192.168.0.105 localhost 127.0.0.1